The surroundings of the apartment building feature well-maintained grassy areas with lush greenery, where benches, playgrounds, and climbing structures for children are situated in its pleasant shade. Its orientation offers beautiful views of the surroundings and ensures a supply of natural light throughout the day. It consists of the following rooms, none of which are through : - living room / 18.3 m2 / with entrance from the hallway and exit to the loggia; - bedroom / 15.4 m2 / accessible from the hallway; - children's room 1 / 11.4 m2 / or office with entrance from the hallway; - children's room 2 / 9.2 m2 / or guest room or study accessible from the kitchen; - kitchen / 12.3 m2 / L-shaped, equipped with a kitchen unit with built-in appliances, refrigerator with freezer, and space for dining seating; - pantry / 1.1 m2 / with access from the kitchen; - bathroom / 3.2 m2 / with sink, bathtub, and washing machine; - toilet / 1.0 m2 / as a separate room with a toilet bowl and sink; - entrance hallway / 8.7 m2 / with access to the toilet, three living rooms, and the kitchen. The spacious loggia / 10.5 m2 / is accessed from the living room. EQUIPMENT AND FURNISHINGS The apartment's furnishings are practical, emphasizing natural decor and the inherent beauty of wood. The property has undergone several reconstructions, the latest of which included the reconstruction of the apartment core and sanitary facilities, replacement of riser pipes, installation of new plastic windows with interior blinds, modernization, and glazing of the loggia. The floor of the apartment features well-preserved wooden parquet and tiles. Above the windows, there are curtain rods with curtains and drapes. The bedroom, children's rooms, and entrance hallway are furnished with wardrobes offering ample storage space. The privacy of the apartment residents is protected by security and fire-resistant entrance doors. The kitchen includes appliances: Mora gas cooker with hood and oven, Whirlpool dishwasher. Appliances, furnishings, and furniture, unless otherwise agreed with the buyer, will remain in the apartment and are included in the sale price. LOCATION The offered property is located in a sought-after area, providing a diverse range of amenities and many other benefits. In close proximity, there are grocery stores and other retail shops, various service establishments, elementary, kindergarten, and secondary schools, a sports center, public garages, and more. The vibrant city center of Žilina is just a 10-minute walk away, as is the beautiful Bôrik city park, offering a rich variety of options for sports and leisure activities. public transport stops with regular connections are located approximately 200 meters from the apartment building. Road access to the expressway for the directions Bratislava - Žilina and Žilina - Čadca is available within 2 minutes. The offered apartment is suitable for a buyer who wants to personally enjoy the advantages of living in the center of the regional city or ensure a financial return on investment through renting out the property.
